         I had a big self and medium EQNecro debate about Demi Lich a while back.  Here is my experience with it.</P><P>I bought Demi Lich for 7k (the going rate at the time) on MM.  I was at the end of level 58.  </P><P>Demi Lich was and still is awesome.  </P><P>Now that I'm 60, I do not use Demi Lich.  </P><P>I believe here is the question you are asking.  Is +1 mana regen for life better then +11 mana for 4 levels (56, 57, 58, 59 - Warlocks use Arch Lich almost exclusivly)?  5% increase in mana regen vs. 50%+ increase in mana regen for 4 levels (your longest levels of your EQ life, ind you).</P><P>I would go for the Demi Lich now and along the way, as you obtain more coin from your adventures, buy the earring later.</P><P><center><BR><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=95266" target="_blank"><h4><font color=red>Kuotat Smith</h4></a>Baroness <s>Warlock</s> Witch<BR>Mithaniel Marr</font id=red><BR></center><BR><a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
