         Being one of those necros who never had Demi until lvl 60.. I gotta say, I'd go with the FT earring. As soon as you hit lvl 60 demi lich is obsolete, the earring will last you a long time. Yes, demi will help you get to 60 faster (only solo really, if you group Lich is fine IMO, its what I did =P)...but its 15k wasted the second you scribe Arch Lich.<BR> I'd rather not get to lvl 60 only to look back at demi lich spell and go "damn, wish I had that 15k to by X item/spell now.. bleh"</P><P><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=34033" target="_blank">http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=34033</a><a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
